            "name": "tool_search",
            "arguments": "{\"query\":\"list available tools\",\"top_k\":10}",
            "output": "{\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"code_interpreter\",\"title\":\"code_interpreter\",\"description\":\"Tool for executing Python code.\\nYou will provide the code to be interpreted and executed. This is useful for tasks that require dynamic code generation\\nand execution, such as data processing, mathematical computations, or any other operations that you cannot perform directly.\\nWhen you send Python code to `python` tool, it runs in a **stateful Jupyter notebook environment**.  \\nThe execution will return results or **time out after 90 seconds** if it exceeds the allowed runtime.  \\n- The `/mnt/data` drive can be used to **save and persist user files**.  \\n- **Internet access is disabled**, meaning external web requests and API calls **will fail**—avoid making them.\",\"inputSchema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"code\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The Python code to execute in the sandboxed container.\\n                    The code should be valid Python syntax and can include imports, file operations,\\n                    data processing, calculations, and visualizations.\"}},\"required\":[\"code\"]},\"_meta\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"file_ids\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"description\":\"List of file IDs to make available in the code execution environment.\\n                    These files can be referenced and used by the Python code.\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"File ID to include in the container\"}},\"model_info\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"description\":\"Information about the model to use for code generation from natural language. If not provided, the model from APIM headers will be used.\",\"properties\":{\"deployment_name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The deployment name of the model.\"},\"model_name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the model.\"},\"model_version\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The version of the model.\"}},\"required\":[\"deployment_na